				<td colspan="2"><span>Thanks for the guide. I've only done fire side so far and didn't know about the cold side mezzers.
<br />

<br />
I'm puzzled by your spell order. &quot;HoS'ing, Snaring, Despelling THEN slowing.&quot;  Aren't you dispelling HoS and snare this way? I start with dispell, hos then slow on the short pulls and dispell, snare on the long pulls, hos as it approaches camp.
<br />

<br />
The biggest problem I have is pulling up and down the stairs. It's like the mobs aren't really chasing, but then they make up for lost time by warping on to me. So I'm casting... oor, oor, oor and then he's on me. Unless they're snared. But groups hate it when you pull with snare because it's a long pull to start with and even longer with snare. But it's survival really.</span></td>
