				<td><img src="/skins/default/images/user_IsOffline.gif" alt="Elfisa is not online. Last active: 2/18/2005 5:32:09 AM" border="0" />&nbsp;<a class="SmallBoldText" href="/User/UserProfile.aspx?UserName=Elfisa">Elfisa</a><br></td>
